name: Way2do | We are what we say!
body:
### Welcome to Way2Do project site

### Authors and Contributors
We invite anyone who is viewing this site to go ahead and contribute to this repo by providing us with links to any good articles, websites or other resources that you come across the Internet.

### Support or Contact
Send us any suggestions or comments that you have in mind.
Feel free to contact us at vachhaniparin@gmail.com 
or at the [Facebook page](http://facebook.com/way2do.net) or at the [Google+ page](https://plus.google.com/+Way2doNet/)
